      • bind

        public <C,T extends C> void bind(java.lang.Class<C> contract,
                                 java.lang.Class<? extends T> implementation)
        Creates a custom binding for a given contract and implementation using a custom AbstractModule. Requires the implementation to extend the contract type.

        The binding is created by Guice, and can be annotated using Guice supported annotations (e.g. Singleton)

        Specified by:

        Type Parameters:
